The paper addresses the algorithmic problem of allocating advertisement space for keywords in sponsored search auctions, which involves game theory (cs.GT), information retrieval (cs.IR), and optimization (cs.DS, cs.LG, cs.AI). The focus on revenue maximization also suggests a connection to economics (cs.EC).
